citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1250 on
30-May-18. I went to the house and knocked on the door. No one answered. I honked my car horn a half dozen
times and did not see anyone around on the property. I called the licensee. She informed me she would not be
home for a while. I informed her I would try back another day.
End of report.

narrative:
2.126(b)
ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1250 on
30-May-18.  I went to the house and knocked on the door.  No one answered.  I honked my car horn a half dozen
times and did not see anyone around on the property.  I called the licensee.  She informed me she would not be
home for a while.  I informed her I would try back another day.
End of report.
